{"tid":1561348,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非要進化, 勇武都要進化 - 訂立\"制約\"","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:39:28.000Z","uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b7652d7bc21262e89761c9c9a9ea5b7eb127dc4","tid":1561348,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"勇武前線係時候要訂立&quot;制約&quot;,去強化每次行動的&quot;攻擊力&quot;<br />\n<br />\n雖然梁天琦講過抗爭無底線,但無系統的勇武只係導致混亂/單純暴力, 參與人數仲要好少,<br />\n後方難以支援<br />\n<br />\n訂立 制約 可以去令勇武行為合理化+常規化,<br />\n作用正如黑警的公安條例,香港鐵路附例,去合理化自己行動<br />\n<br />\n至於 制約 內容 可以係<br />\n-黑警使用武力先用火魔法<br />\n-黨鐵封站/運兵先&quot;做野&quot;對抗黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n目的都係令勇武行動融入市民心中, 令更多前線知道要做咩,定立所謂&quot;清晰指引&quot;"},{"pid":"40ee05684b15f2a33071d211c9ad1d26b45ff4df","tid":1561348,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ef6d6b9fc37e1385e6c63a466fc36c329cba70ed","tid":1561348,"uid":297356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"f151c95894bde68379ab85344fee0ef7bb6c2665","tid":1561348,"uid":310877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d67bd6f6c4e259c4f